Subject: [PATCH 001/353] arm64: defconfig: Add or edit needed features for
 Renesas SOC

1. Add:
	- PCIe
	- AVB
	- CAN
	- IPMMU
	- MSIOF
	- Thermal
	- GPIO
	- PTP clock
	- VIN

2. Change from kernel module to built-in drivers:
	- AUDIO/SSI
	- DU
	- PWM/TPU
	- USB2.0 Function

Signed-off-by: Hien Huynh <hien.huynh.px@renesas.com>
